  <brief_title>A Pharmacokinetic Evaluation of Metformin in Relation to the Polymorphism A270S in Healthy Caucasian Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pharmacokinetic Evaluation of Metformin in Relation to the Polymorphism A270S in Healthy Caucasian Volunteers.</official_title>
