  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate the pharmacokinetics of metformin in healthy Caucasians
      volunteers with and without the polymorphism A270S in OCT2,thus the study hypothesis is that
      renal clearance of metformin is affected in Caucasian with the known single nucleotide
      polymorphisms A270S in OCT2.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
